        {
            "id": 6007239,
            "title": "〈台幣〉亞幣走勢不同調 終止連3貶又升回29字頭",
            "description": "<main class=\"c1tt5pk2\" id=\"article-container\" style=\"--c1tt5pk2-0:20px\"><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p><a href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/index/GI/DXY\">美元指數</a> 3 日擺脫頹勢展開反彈，主要亞幣普遍回檔，<a href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/forex/detail/usdtwd\">新台幣</a>兌美元今 (4) 日受到出口商拋匯影響，又升回 29 字頭，終場升值 5.3 分，收在 29.952 元，終止連 3 貶，台北及元太外匯市場總成交值 17.915 億美元，整體交投仍偏清淡。</p></section><p></p><div class=\"c1hvmcli\"><figure><div class=\"iirgi4a\"><img alt=\"cover image of news article\" class=\"cr8g41v\" data-nimg=\"fill\" decoding=\"async\" fetchpriority=\"high\" sizes=\"\n            (max-width: 1024px) 100% 406px,\n            (max-width: 768px) 100% 193px\n          \" src=\"/_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6007239%2Fl%2Fc80dc92d27301a4d441c4448ce44574e.jpg&amp;w=3840&amp;q=75\" srcset=\"/_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6007239%2Fl%2Fc80dc92d27301a4d441c4448ce44574e.jpg&amp;w=16&amp;q=75 16w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6007239%2Fl%2Fc80dc92d27301a4d441c4448ce44574e.jpg&amp;w=32&amp;q=75 32w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6007239%2Fl%2Fc80dc92d27301a4d441c4448ce44574e.jpg&amp;w=48&amp;q=75 48w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6007239%2Fl%2Fc80dc92d27301a4d441c4448ce44574e.jpg&amp;w=64&amp;q=75 64w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6007239%2Fl%2Fc80dc92d27301a4d441c4448ce44574e.jpg&amp;w=96&amp;q=75 96w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6007239%2Fl%2Fc80dc92d27301a4d441c4448ce44574e.jpg&amp;w=128&amp;q=75 128w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6007239%2Fl%2Fc80dc92d27301a4d441c4448ce44574e.jpg&amp;w=256&amp;q=75 256w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6007239%2Fl%2Fc80dc92d27301a4d441c4448ce44574e.jpg&amp;w=384&amp;q=75 384w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6007239%2Fl%2Fc80dc92d27301a4d441c4448ce44574e.jpg&amp;w=640&amp;q=75 640w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6007239%2Fl%2Fc80dc92d27301a4d441c4448ce44574e.jpg&amp;w=750&amp;q=75 750w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6007239%2Fl%2Fc80dc92d27301a4d441c4448ce44574e.jpg&amp;w=828&amp;q=75 828w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6007239%2Fl%2Fc80dc92d27301a4d441c4448ce44574e.jpg&amp;w=1080&amp;q=75 1080w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6007239%2Fl%2Fc80dc92d27301a4d441c4448ce44574e.jpg&amp;w=1200&amp;q=75 1200w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6007239%2Fl%2Fc80dc92d27301a4d441c4448ce44574e.jpg&amp;w=1920&amp;q=75 1920w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6007239%2Fl%2Fc80dc92d27301a4d441c4448ce44574e.jpg&amp;w=2048&amp;q=75 2048w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6007239%2Fl%2Fc80dc92d27301a4d441c4448ce44574e.jpg&amp;w=3840&amp;q=75 3840w\" style=\"position:absolute;height:100%;width:100%;left:0;top:0;right:0;bottom:0;color:transparent\"/></div><figcaption class=\"c1gcnfq1\">〈台幣〉亞幣走勢不同調 終止連3貶又升回29字頭。(圖：shutterstock)</figcaption></figure></div><section style=\"margin-top:30px\">\n</section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p><a href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/forex/detail/usdtwd\">新台幣</a>兌美元今天以 30.02 元開盤，最高升抵 29.933 元，外匯交易員指出，滿手美元的出口商近期穩定掛單賣匯，因此，匯價在 30 元附近壓力相當大，外資操作並無明確方向，但台股強勢走高，外資今天確實也有較多匯入，相對而言，買匯力道較為空虛。</p></section><section>\n</section><!--$--><!--/$--><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>觀察主要亞幣今天表現，根據央行統計，<a href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/forex/detail/jpyusd\">日元</a>重挫 0.88%，新加坡幣貶值 0.23%，<a href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/forex/detail/cnyusd\">人民幣</a>小貶 0.01%；<a href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/forex/detail/krwusd\">韓元</a>方面，由於韓國選出新總統李在明，<a href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/forex/detail/krwusd\">韓元</a>逆勢升值 0.37%，<a href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/forex/detail/usdtwd\">新台幣</a>亦升值 0.18%，表現相對較強。</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\">\n</section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>聯準會 (Fed) 決策官員預計將於 6 月 17 至 18 日舉行 FOMC 會議，決定最新利率政策，市場屏息以待，由於美國經濟基本面仍然穩健，期貨市場普遍押注此次將按兵不動，不過，有官員透露，若近期貿易政策的不確定性得以化解，Fed 還是有可能啟動降息。</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\">\n</section></main>",
