            "title": "小非農就業數據不振！川普再度向鮑爾施壓 呼籲Fed立刻降息",
            "description": "<main class=\"c1tt5pk2\" id=\"article-container\" style=\"--c1tt5pk2-0:20px\"><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>美國總統川普周三 (4 日) 在有「小非農」之稱的 ADP 最新就業報告公布後，再度對聯準會 (Fed) 主席鮑爾開砲，敦促其降息以提振經濟。</p></section><p></p><div class=\"c1hvmcli\"><figure><div class=\"iirgi4a\"><img alt=\"cover image of news article\" class=\"cr8g41v\" data-nimg=\"fill\" decoding=\"async\" fetchpriority=\"high\" sizes=\"\n            (max-width: 1024px) 100% 406px,\n            (max-width: 768px) 100% 193px\n          \" src=\"/_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6007242%2Fl%2Fc5c31e473fea60866a91a05207100a59.jpg&amp;w=3840&amp;q=75\" srcset=\"/_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6007242%2Fl%2Fc5c31e473fea60866a91a05207100a59.jpg&amp;w=16&amp;q=75 16w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6007242%2Fl%2Fc5c31e473fea60866a91a05207100a59.jpg&amp;w=32&amp;q=75 32w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6007242%2Fl%2Fc5c31e473fea60866a91a05207100a59.jpg&amp;w=48&amp;q=75 48w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6007242%2Fl%2Fc5c31e473fea60866a91a05207100a59.jpg&amp;w=64&amp;q=75 64w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6007242%2Fl%2Fc5c31e473fea60866a91a05207100a59.jpg&amp;w=96&amp;q=75 96w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6007242%2Fl%2Fc5c31e473fea60866a91a05207100a59.jpg&amp;w=128&amp;q=75 128w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6007242%2Fl%2Fc5c31e473fea60866a91a05207100a59.jpg&amp;w=256&amp;q=75 256w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6007242%2Fl%2Fc5c31e473fea60866a91a05207100a59.jpg&amp;w=384&amp;q=75 384w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6007242%2Fl%2Fc5c31e473fea60866a91a05207100a59.jpg&amp;w=640&amp;q=75 640w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6007242%2Fl%2Fc5c31e473fea60866a91a05207100a59.jpg&amp;w=750&amp;q=75 750w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6007242%2Fl%2Fc5c31e473fea60866a91a05207100a59.jpg&amp;w=828&amp;q=75 828w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6007242%2Fl%2Fc5c31e473fea60866a91a05207100a59.jpg&amp;w=1080&amp;q=75 1080w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6007242%2Fl%2Fc5c31e473fea60866a91a05207100a59.jpg&amp;w=1200&amp;q=75 1200w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6007242%2Fl%2Fc5c31e473fea60866a91a05207100a59.jpg&amp;w=1920&amp;q=75 1920w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6007242%2Fl%2Fc5c31e473fea60866a91a05207100a59.jpg&amp;w=2048&amp;q=75 2048w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6007242%2Fl%2Fc5c31e473fea60866a91a05207100a59.jpg&amp;w=3840&amp;q=75 3840w\" style=\"position:absolute;height:100%;width:100%;left:0;top:0;right:0;bottom:0;color:transparent\"/></div><figcaption class=\"c1gcnfq1\">小非農就業數據不振！川普再度向鮑爾施壓 呼籲Fed立刻降息(圖：REUTERS/TPG)</figcaption></figure></div><section style=\"margin-top:30px\">\n</section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>根據 ADP 最新數據，美國 5 月民間新增就業僅 3.7 萬人，創下逾兩年新低，顯示勞動市場放緩跡象。川普隨後在 Truth Social 平台上怒批鮑爾。</p></section><section>\n</section><!--$--><!--/$--><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>川普寫道：「ADP 數據出爐了！！！『慢郎中』(Too Late) 鮑爾現在必須降息。他真是令人難以置信！！！歐洲已經降息九次了！」</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\">\n</section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><figure><img alt=\"圖：川普Truth Social\" data-height=\"222\" data-mime=\"image/jpeg\" data-ratio=\"3.4234234234234235\" data-src-m=\"https://cimg.cnyes.cool/prod/news/6007242/m/f4ab3c336b2a13c164742d99557f228c.jpg\" data-width=\"760\" src=\"https://cimg.cnyes.cool/prod/news/6007242/l/f4ab3c336b2a13c164742d99557f228c.jpg\"/>\n<figcaption>圖：川普 Truth Social</figcaption>\n</figure></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\">\n</section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>持續更新...</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\">\n</section></main>",
